# ── Common base — OS · editors · env · logs · temp ───────────────────────────
# Vendored & curated from github/gitignore (Global/*) — CC0-1.0 (public domain).
# Source: https://github.com/github/gitignore  ·  applies to ANY stack.
# RULE: never add a lockfile here — lockfiles are COMMITTED for reproducible installs.
# RULE: no trailing comments on a pattern line (a "# ..." becomes part of the pattern).

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Linux
*~
.fuse_hidden*
.directory
.Trash-*

# Editors / IDEs (keep shared VSCode config; ignore the rest)
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.swp
*.swo
*.sublime-workspace

# Environment / secrets — commit a .env.example, never real secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Logs & temp
*.log
logs/
*.tmp
*.temp
.cache/
tmp/
